{"tid":54284,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"做左8年廚師，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-25T11:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T11:43:00.000Z","uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a52d16a9df6fb6d2744720037a1156109198daa","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"飲食問題盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8220324fa63fca04e317c7e55264c199ddfb1da","tid":54284,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"點睇林小小"},{"pid":"7bcd9e694b4adacede0ff5180545686fea72fa82","tid":54284,"uid":20373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"中定西"},{"pid":"e061e5677d5429f632ec3a8eadafe73599453cf8","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇林小小</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心覺得佢本人係識煮野食既！"},{"pid":"f4ba3ec0487b5497a5fb033e9ff5b4d92875b622","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中定西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西"},{"pid":"aaee96d2fb41419357f7c44d5ed61c9871e599b0","tid":54284,"uid":20373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中定西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店？<br />\n咁覺得中廚有咩比西廚優勝"},{"pid":"6d240f716103280f223c54103ec2ef28df72307e","tid":54284,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"鼎爺勁唔勁"},{"pid":"44e866e27bd83b43757f8f48acd46888268e5827","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中定西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店？<br />\n咁覺得中廚有咩比西廚優勝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平均人工比西廚高，學廚嘅時候分工比較仔細，通常你學做一個位嘅時候通常都要一年半載先至可以轉，基本上可以睇晒成個廚房嘅運作，西餐通常凍，熱，甜會比較清楚，其次我覺得中餐好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acefbd6fcb707f3295dc7faa058d7dd5f2374543","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼎爺勁唔勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f71907844e1e9bea77634f27d5b77eb18abde2","tid":54284,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中定西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問你自己整面撈嘅方法係點"},{"pid":"cbbf83a5e4912deb496e22fec8dadb0f20d2f30e","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中定西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問你自己整面撈嘅方法係點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你點用，我個人比較喜歡先煮牛油清煮都夠熱，之後直接加麵粉，再落熱水煮到夠身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7223908b0f1b6b0042dd6e81341863bd0935c7c5","tid":54284,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"做左八年 做酒店定街檔<br />\n同埋依家咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3ef4770a0d774c22338afaf56f278661048e8","tid":54284,"uid":35971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:49:49.000Z","msg":"通常公司俾你乜嘢待遇？"},{"pid":"e38fffcd5d8ffb1654765f60d5fe031de702a25a","tid":54284,"uid":30171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"有冇試過在仆街西客份餐度加料？"},{"pid":"890eb2728f89ae6387fb5366dfeac31718a5fa8f","tid":54284,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"識唔識煮錦繡多味魚？"},{"pid":"996b6f9701fc8cc8761392d6b31980695f6429f1","tid":54284,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5877e0d9da1977b19b320368912d9493095db89","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左八年 做酒店定街檔<br />\n同埋依家咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左5年酒店，3年街檔，依家SeniorA一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa30e39f2c6b623a58f75ffd3f2edcbc186f9e42","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常公司俾你乜嘢待遇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n12日大假，12日努工假，醫療津貼，年尾有花紅咁樣囉，餐廳就慘啲，基本上多數係八日大假"},{"pid":"6ce655b8586d2fa3522ec20da9efc480700b21a3","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過在仆街西客份餐度加料？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒，根本忙到冇時間做依啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常係樓面做"},{"pid":"f521462387ed1ddee5ff2e87e2b10d265f85f7dc","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識唔識煮錦繡多味魚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講要去中華廚藝學院學師"},{"pid":"afa593ec72732ba329383b0df04ab4cc0b1d19e4","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒，基本上我16歲開始就做廚師，可能我真心鍾意煮飯，所以到而家都冇諗過會辭職"},{"pid":"301e99a4e6b46d61fedef3ef99de0583788318a2","tid":54284,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做左八年 做酒店定街檔<br />\n同埋依家咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左5年酒店，3年街檔，依家SeniorA一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一上demi個價又高一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 你果間幾星"},{"pid":"9e90fc11ecd1b796104b20323bae459dc59f4525","tid":54284,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"白汁點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b651a4a7552444f925092784626d59477dde5ef9","tid":54284,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做左八年 做酒店定街檔<br />\n同埋依家咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左5年酒店，3年街檔，依家SeniorA一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一上demi個價又高一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 你果間幾星</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4-5星，其實價位差唔多，最緊要唔洗落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b13544df303a494a69d855b2a5e55c9b91e2c4","tid":54284,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左5年酒店，3年街檔，依家SeniorA一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一上demi個價又高一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 你果間幾星</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4-5星，其實價位差唔多，最緊要唔洗落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忙嘅大位都要落架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個手足一上demi即刻多三千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}